0.9.name: wordpress/dublin-core-metadata
0.9.description: This plugin allows a user to specifiy which parts of the dublin core namespace they wish to use and then adds extra fields to the post / page pages to allow for submissions of this data. For support please see http://www.pgogy.com and http://www.pgogy.com/code/groups/wordpress/dublin-core-metadata/
